    Source

    public class BackfillHiveSource
extends HiveAvroToOrcSource
    A HiveSource used to create workunits without a watermark check. #shouldCreateWorkunit(long, LongWatermark) will always return true

    • Field Detail

      • BACKFILL_SOURCE_PARTITION_WHITELIST_KEY

        public static final String BACKFILL_SOURCE_PARTITION_WHITELIST_KEY
        A comma separated list of Partition.getCompleteName()s that need backfill. If not set, all partitions will be backfilled

        E.g. service@logEvent@datepartition=2016-08-04-00,service@logEvent@datepartition=2016-08-05-00
